<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>URGENT: Monthly Report Due Soon</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background: #f7fafc; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #dc2626; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 15px; font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px; color: #718096; font-size: 12px; }
    .urgent-box { background: #fee2e2; padding: 15px; border-left: 4px solid #dc2626; margin: 15px 0; }
    .countdown { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #dc2626; text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>URGENT: Report Deadline Approaching!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

      <div class="urgent-box">
        <strong>URGENT:</strong> Your monthly report for <strong>{{month}} {{year}}</strong> is due in <strong>{{daysLeft}} days</strong>!
      </div>

      <div class="countdown">
        Only {{daysLeft}} days left!
      </div>

      <p>Please submit your monthly internship report immediately to avoid any issues with your internship record.</p>

      <p>Late submissions may affect:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Your internship progress tracking</li>
        <li>Faculty evaluation reports</li>
        <li>Final internship completion certificate</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <a href="{{reportUrl}}" class="button">Submit Report NOW</a>
      </p>

      <p>If you're facing any difficulties in submitting the report, please contact your faculty mentor immediately.</p>

      <p>Best regards,<br>College Management System</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated urgent reminder. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
